          * Real Favicon

        h5 Build Tools
        pre.prettyprint.lang-html.

          * CSSMin
          * Uglify
          * HTML minify
          * ImageMin
          * Concat 

        h5 Test Tools

        pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
          * Browserify
          * BrowserSync
          * Phantom
          * Karma


        h3 Install Project 

        pre.prettyprint.lang-html. 
          Windows: run file `install.bat`

        pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
          MAC/Ubuntu: run file `sh install.sh` 

        h3 Update Project

        pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
          Windows: run file `update.bat`

        pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
          MAC/Ubuntu: run file `sh update.sh` 

        h3 Upgrade & Check Missing package

        pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
          run `npm run check`

        h3 Config 

        pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
          Config file `config.yml`

        h3 Working in Project

        pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
          Test: run `npm run test`

        pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
          Serve: run `npm run serve`

        pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
          Build: run `npm run pro`

        pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
          Dev: run `npm run dev`

        pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
          Tools: run `npm run tool`

